{"word":"G2856 - κολοβόω - kolobóō - kol-ob-o'-o - Shorten","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κολοβόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kolobóō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kol-ob-o'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Shorten</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - குறைத்திரு"},{"paragraph":"to cut off to shorten, abridge, curtail"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a derivative of the base of <a href=\"#/G2849 - κολάζω - kolázō - kol-ad'-zo/2849\">G2849</a>; to <i>dock</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>abridge:</i> - shorten.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}